Hello,=C2=A0


Thanks for trying out Windsurf! We=E2=80=99ve just released=C2=A0[SWE-1.5](=
https://cognition.ai/blog/swe-1-5), the latest in our family of models opti=
mized for software engineering. SWE-1.5 beats GPT-5-high on SWE-Bench Pro a=
nd achieves speeds of up to ~6x faster than Haiku 4.5, ~13x faster than Son=
net 4.5, and ~3x faster than Composer 1.


[Upgrade to Pro](https://windsurf.com/subscription/manage-plan)=C2=A0to try=
 it!


We believe that developers shouldn=E2=80=99t have to choose between speed a=
nd intelligence.


-=20

On October 16, we released Fast Context powered by=C2=A0SWE-grep, an agenti=
c model that powers rapid context engineering.


-=20

Today, SWE-1.5 reimagines the entire stack (model, inference, and agent har=
ness) as a unified system optimized for both.


We=E2=80=99ve also recently shipped a number of patches around bug fixes an=
d stability. You can read about them in our=C2=A0[Changelog](https://windsu=
rf.com/changelog).


SWE-1.5, Fast Context, and much more are now available in Windsurf Pro. We=
=E2=80=99d love for you to try them!


Windsurf Team


